  {name: "2 Turtle Doves", description: "2 Turtle Doves is the second in the 12 Days/Years of Christmas Series. We decided to take our inspiration from the name and base the beer on the \"turtle\" candy, brewing it with cocoa nibs, toasted pecans, caramelized sugar and a lot of caramel malts. Somewhere between a Belgian-style Dark Strong Ale and an Imperial Porter, this beer is designed to take the journey through time until 12 Drummers Drumming.", abv: "12", img: nil, avg_score: nil, user_id: nil, brewery_id: nil, availability_id: nil, type_id: 64, brewery_db_id: "oRrA7s"},
